Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們會去春香家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊  今天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  保阪學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的人是我  速水學姐和淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人請您去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和南春香甚至還沒說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有理由會請我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好這人至少還能想明白這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須先做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣和她搭話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離放學沒多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動必須要有計劃性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您試圖在放學前成為春香的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐  有點兒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要告訴那男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我們要去春香家？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人現在也想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他盯上春香了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼有趣的事你怎麼不早說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫春香來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐不能指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能由我來保護春香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她遠離那惡棍的魔爪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…保阪學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪的模擬場景\N雨中邂逅篇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣南春香就會不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時我就露出醉人的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐  什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪的模擬場景\N公園的雪中約會篇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣南春香就會羞得低下頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時我就將她摟入懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就是之後要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在於…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  您是為了和她交朋友才有這模擬場景的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我愛你」和「我喜歡你」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一句比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:38.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：敬體句和簡體句的差別而已）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？有什麼不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫「有什麼不同」  當然有很大不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細聽好了
