Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  情不自禁就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還嚼得不夠充分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬著自己了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別來這一套
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一副覺得可憐兮兮的樣子看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你倒不是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這垃圾食品玩弄了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在嘴裏留下了傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被親妹妹認為是可悲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是屈辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是本集最大的屈辱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你怎麼吹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要哭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  情不自禁就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  現在開始特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是沒有半點吹泡泡糖的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  我再給你示範一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  泡泡糖？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連春香都會？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是吹泡泡這麼簡單…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在已有的一層泡泡裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹出第二層的高等技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是春香姐姐
