Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說南春香廚藝很出色？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我常去吃她的便當
