Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓她分給你一些？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過  讓她分便當給一個從來沒有說過話的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛慕虛榮的小人物也是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用這麼出人意料的言語來形容我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去  直接找她談談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼狠拍我的背
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去卡嚓卡嚓  嘩啦嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識的見正是魅力的魅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：日文這兩個詞中兩個字讀音相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這是在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希不在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明顯就是在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還準備了共通的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共通的話題？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烹飪方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長喜歡做菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果南春香說很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就應該是有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香說的絕對是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她說烏鴉是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把世上所有的烏鴉染白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好這人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實挺酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:13:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是該脫的時候吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還是應該漂白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長  這下就全曝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  南春香上哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真希一同去買麵包了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道南春香不是自己帶便當來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  但是今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都吃麵包是會營養失調的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐把所有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候就得有志於烹飪的我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都說了  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  南春香！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛把春香的便當吃了個精光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希也要多吃些  長得高高大大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（第二天）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？保阪你今天帶便當來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有兩份一樣的便當？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法式風味的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不能送給她吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅葡萄酒的調味也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp1}Saute{\fsp63}　{\r}\N葡萄乾也好嫩煎肉也好  甚至於我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都太不成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp17}　{\fsp1}Estragon{\fsp159}　{\fsp1}Caper{\r}\N就著蛋黃醬茵陳蒿和醃黃瓜非常有馬檳榔的風味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得給她做出最好的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（星期一）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電飯煲不是空空如也嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗好後明明按了開關的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這遞到你面前的飯碗要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期一不吃早飯就沒有力氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我留心一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是還有麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道還有麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去烤一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我去烤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是沒吃早飯沒有力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪不開口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去還是不錯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沸騰的熱水中加鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp28}　{\fsp1}Pasta{\r}\N放入意大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攪拌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說話也很怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說春香她現在很餓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是為了這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會每日準備兩份便當的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是打算減肥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香怎麼可能不知道飲食健康的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  就算略有那麼一點兒胖…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會為她訂製一套健康瘦身的食譜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們倆一起出謀劃策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一來終於  屬於兩人的夢想誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  吃飯去吃飯去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了令人噁心的企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有些飯團  你要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把箔紙撕下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就不必出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她能好好地吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉上能一直保有笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你都做了什麼  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她居然煮了米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？星期一本來是吃意大利面的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你們肯定想吃米飯了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:38.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Super Roman）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(20,20)\fs18}廣告產品\N澳洲產\N火鍋用牛肉\N100g\N198日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧一瞧看一看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很便宜的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有活蹦亂跳的鮮魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(20,20)\fs18}只限今日\N鱈魚\N6980日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪的模擬場景\N幸福的去向篇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱈魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及豆腐  冬菇  白菜都歸我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你是讓本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃茼蒿菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該先說「我開動了」吧  女兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使用上這條魚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的南春香也不會露出笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會做出配得上你的終極便當
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那可真是有趣極了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.83,0:21:38.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說這位小哥  你這樣我很為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(20,20)\fs18}牛裏脊  火鍋料\N澳洲產\N254克\N502日元\N童夢牧場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就吃牛肉火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.07,0:00:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我談談南春香的魅力？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  我是說預告…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就先回顧一下我這半輩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是帶著繫在小指上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一頭連著南春香的紅絲線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這個世界上的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  三姐妹的雲雨陰晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預告您也照脫不誤啊

